Từ điển Anh - Việt
 ■Xem tear

Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
torn
▸ adjective
1a torn shirt: RIPPED, rent, cut, slit; ragged, tattered, in tatters, in ribbons.
2she was torn between the two options: WAVERING, vacillating, irresolute, dithering, uncertain, unsure, undecided, in two minds.

Kết hợp từ & Cấu trúc câu
torn
adj.
divided
(cannot stand alone) torn between (he was torn between his family and his job)
